'''早產'''（'''preterm birth、premature birth'''），主要是指[[胎兒|胎兒]]在早於37週之前[[分娩|分娩]]的過程<ref name=NIH2014Def>{{cite web|title=Preterm Labor and Birth: Condition Information|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/preterm/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|website=http://www.nichd.nih.gov|accessdate=2015-03-07|date=03/11/2014|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402111534/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/preterm/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其嬰兒被稱為早產兒（{{lang|en|preemies, premmies}}<ref name=NIH2014Def/>）。早產的症狀包含每次[[子宮收縮|子宮收縮]]間隔少於10分鐘，或液體從陰道流出<ref>{{cite web|title=What are the symptoms of preterm labor?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/preterm/conditioninfo/Pages/symptoms.aspx|website=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/|accessdate=2015-03-07|date=11/06/2013|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402154200/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/preterm/conditioninfo/Pages/symptoms.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。早產兒會有[[腦性麻痺|腦性麻痺]]、{{link-en|發展遲緩|Developmental disability}}、[[聾|聽力]]與[[視力障礙|視力障礙]]等巨大風險，越早出生則風險越大<ref name=NIH2014Def/>。

早產的原因尚不明朗<ref name=WHO2014>{{cite web |url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs363/en/ |title=Preterm birth Fact sheet N°363 |author=World Health Organization |work=who.int |date=November 2014 |accessdate=2015-03-06 |archive-date=2015-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150307050438/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs363/en/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其風險因子包含[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]、[[高血壓|高血壓]]、懷有多於1個胎兒、[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]或[[體重不足|體重不足]]、一系列[[陰道炎|陰道炎]]、[[吸菸|吸菸]]與{{link-en|壓力 (心理學)|Stress (psychological)|心理壓力}}等等<ref name=WHO2014/><ref>{{cite web|title=What are the risk factors for preterm labor and birth?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/preterm/conditioninfo/Pages/who_risk.aspx|website=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/|accessdate=2015-03-07|date=03/11/2014|archive-date=2015-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150405075659/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/preterm/conditioninfo/Pages/who_risk.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除非有其他醫療狀況如[[妊娠毒血症|妊娠毒血症]]<ref>{{cite web|title=What causes preterm labor and birth?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/preterm/conditioninfo/Pages/causes.aspx|website=http://www.nichd.nih.gov|accessdate=2015-03-07|date=03/11/2014|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402165739/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/preterm/conditioninfo/Pages/causes.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，孕期直到39週以前不建議採取[[引產|引產]]等提前分娩措施，對於[[剖腹產|剖腹產]]而言也適用這樣的建議<ref name=WHO2014/>。

對於高風險孕婦而言，在懷孕期間採用[[孕酮|孕酮]]可預防早產，而臥床休息並無法避免早產<ref name=NIH2014Pre>{{cite web|title=What treatments are used to prevent preterm labor and birth?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/preterm/conditioninfo/Pages/treatments.aspx|website=http://www.nichd.nih.gov|accessdate=2015-03-07|date=03/11/2014|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402122124/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/preterm/conditioninfo/Pages/treatments.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。估計至少75%早產兒可藉由適當治療而存活<ref name=WHO2014/>。於24-34週之間分娩的婦女可藉由[[皮質類固醇|皮質類固醇]]提高預後成效<ref name=NIH2013Mg>{{cite web|title=What treatments can reduce the chances of preterm labor & birth?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/preterm/conditioninfo/Pages/reduce.aspx|website=http://www.nichd.nih.gov|accessdate=2015-03-07|date=11/06/2013|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402102224/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/preterm/conditioninfo/Pages/reduce.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一系列藥物如[[硝苯地平|硝苯地平]]可以讓母親延遲分娩，期能後送至提供更多醫療照護的場域，且能使皮質類固醇發揮更大功效<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Haram|first1=K|last2=Mortensen|first2=JH|last3=Morrison|first3=JC|title=Tocolysis for acute preterm labor: does anything work.|journal=The journal of maternal-fetal & neonatal medicine : the official journal of the European Association of Perinatal Medicine, the Federation of Asia and Oceania Perinatal Societies, the International Society of Perinatal Obstetricians|date=2014-07-03|pages=1-8|pmid=24990666}}</ref>。一旦嬰兒出生，必須進行一系列護理措施，包含藉由肌膚間接觸使嬰兒保暖、[[母乳餵養|母乳餵養]]協助、[[感染|感染]]治療與呼吸協助<ref name=WHO2014/>。

早產是全球各地嬰兒最常見死因<ref name=NIH2014Def/>，每年有將近1,500萬的早產兒出生，約占所有生產的5-18%。1990到2010年代，許多國家的嬰兒早產率都有上升趨勢<ref name=WHO2014/>。早產相關併發症，相較於1990年造成157萬名嬰兒死亡，2013年降低到了74萬名<ref name=GDB2013>{{cite journal|last1=GBD 2013 Mortality and Causes of Death|first1=Collaborators|title=Global, regional, and national age-sex specific all-cause and cause-specific mortality for 240 causes of death, 1990-2013: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2013.|journal=Lancet|date=2014-12-17|pmid=25530442|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(14)61682-2}}</ref>。23周以前出生的嬰兒，存活率幾乎為零；懷孕23周出生的早產兒存活率為15%，24周為55%，25周存活率則接近八成<ref>{{cite book|last1=Cloherty|first1=John P.|title=Manual of neonatal care|date=2012|publisher=Wolters Kluwer Health/Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|location=Philadelphia|isbn=9781608317776|page=146|edition=7th ed.|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=xnTkX0q63CsC&pg=PT146|chapter=Care of the Extremely Low Birth Weight Infant|access-date=2015-07-13|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520010824/https://books.google.ca/books?id=xnTkX0q63CsC&pg=PT146|dead-url=no}}</ref>。週數較大的早產兒，之後的相關併發症也較少<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Jarjour|first1=IT|title=Neurodevelopmental Outcome After Extreme Prematurity: A Review of the Literature.|journal=Pediatric neurology|date=February 2015|volume=52|issue=2|pages=143-152|pmid=25497122}}</ref>。
